rows.label: qst300306_msg003

rows.label: qst300306_msg004

rows.label: qst300306_msg005
rows.name:
Response 1: ...Yes. Is there a
problem with being from Superbia?

rows.label: qst300306_msg006
rows.name: Response 2: ...That's a secret.

rows.label: qst300306_msg007
rows.name: Response 3: ...That's a secret.

rows.label: qst300306_msg008
rows.name: Ask for more details (FS)

rows.label: qst300306_msg009
rows.name: Response 1: Continued

rows.label: qst300306_msg010
rows.name: Response 2: Continued

rows.label: qst300306_msg011
rows.name: Response 3: Continued

rows.label: qst300306_msg0001
rows.name:
Zengrid Cathedra...[ML:Dash ] My
full name is longer, but
you may call me Zengrid.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0002
rows.name: Ah, no. Please call me that.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0003
rows.name:
I am from Fons Maim, and my house is
an old noble one, but now that it has
declined, I am just a commoner.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0004
rows.name:
I have experience surviving
difficult situations. You can
leave the money management to me.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0005
rows.name: Then, I'll ask you some questions.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0006
rows.name:
Hehe, ask me anything...[ML:Dash ]
Um, please don't hesitate.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0051
rows.name: What should I ask?

rows.label: qst300306_msg0052
rows.name: Motivation

rows.label: qst300306_msg0053
rows.name: Skills

rows.label: qst300306_msg0054
rows.name: Future goals

rows.label: qst300306_msg0055
rows.name: Nothing in particular

rows.label: qst300306_msg0101
rows.name: I need money...[ML:Dash ] I mean, yes.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0102
rows.name: Are there any circumstances?

rows.label: qst300306_msg0103
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]My house was an old noble one, but
it declined when I was a child.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0104
rows.name: To restore my house, I need money.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0105
rows.name:
Now, you will hire me!
[ML:Dash ]No, please hire me.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0201
rows.name:
I have lost my home and my fortune.
All that remains is a long name and
the ability to raise funds.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0202
rows.name: Could you tell me more specifically?

rows.label: qst300306_msg0203
rows.name:
When I was young, I lived
a good life as a noble.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0204
rows.name:
Therefore, I have the ability to
distinguish things of good quality.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0205
rows.name:
In other words, I can acquire
cheap and truly good items
and avoid wasting money.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0301
rows.name:
I am aiming to restore my
house. I cannot let it end
with my generation.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0302
rows.name:
What are your goals
for this Merc Group?

rows.label: qst300306_msg0303
rows.name:
I want to eliminate waste and run
things in a smart and elegant way.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0304
rows.name:
I've been watching for a while since I arrived,
and there are many wasteful aspects in how
weapons, food, and supplies are used.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0305
rows.name:
The number of people has increased
rapidly, so you must be too busy
to pay attention to the details.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0401
rows.name: Well, that concludes the interview.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0402
rows.name:
We will inform you of the results
later, so you may go now.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0403
rows.name:
You will lose out if you don't
hire me...[ML:Dash ] I'm sorry, I still
can't shake my noble air...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst300306_msg0404
rows.name:
Um, that's all the candidates. You need
time to think about who to hire, right?
Let me know when you've decided.

rows.label: qst300306_msg0501
rows.name:
Is there anything else
you'd like to ask?
